    <item>
      <title>中国淡化2024年大规模刺激措施，考验投资者耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-downplays-big-stimulus-in-2024-testing-investor-patience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强发出了迄今为止最明确的信号，即在数十年来最严重的通缩浪潮中，北京不会采取大规模刺激措施来重振增长。另一批令人不安的数据正在考验投资者的耐心，他们担心北京方面落后于形势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-downplays-big-stimulus-in-2024-testing-investor-patience</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国将在提高塔卡利率的同时引入爬行挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行表示，正在考虑引入爬行钉住汇率制度以保持本国货币稳定，同时提高了关键利率并缩小了利率走廊以应对顽固的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
